## Results policy
# Do NOT blanket-ignore results. We want CSV/PNG/JSON/LOG/TXT artifacts checked in
# (especially for overnight runs). Checkpoints stay ignored via patterns below.

# Ensure logs under results are included (overrides the global *.log ignore above)
!results/**/*.log
!results/**/*.csv
!results/**/*.png
!results/**/*.json
!results/**/*.jsonl
!results/**/*.txt
!results/**/*.md
# local secrets
.secrets/
.env
